            <abstract>
                <p><foreign xml:lang="gez">Qǝne</foreign> without type indication in the manuscript. It consists of six rhymed lines
                    (although these do not correspond to the lines in the manuscript layout), 
                    meaning
                    that it might be classified as a <foreign xml:lang="gez">śǝllāse qǝne</foreign> according to
                    <bibl><ptr target="bm:Guidi1900Qene"/></bibl>. 
                    It is attributed to <persName ref="PRS14579WaldaGabreel"/> in the manuscript.</p>
            </abstract>
