            <div type="edition" xml:lang="gez">
                <note>This edition is based on <ref type="mss" corresp="UppQ1524o"/> on fols 1r, 2r.
                    Division into verses is indicated with ፤ .
                    The end of the poem is indicated with ። .
                    The first line was originally laid out as four lines in the manuscript, each ending with ፤ .
                However, later this was noted and the lines were marked as constituting a single line by a speaker of
                Swedish (who noted down <foreign xml:lang="sv">"1 rad"</foreign>, "one line").
                Judging from the rhyme, lines 3, 4, and 5 also appear to have been divided—each into two lines—but this has not
                been noted in the manuscript.</note>
                <ab>
                    <l n="1">ዓለም፡ እስከ፡ ጊዜሃ<choice><sic>፤</sic><corr resp="JK">፡</corr></choice>
                        በሐብለ፡ ዝንጋኤ፡ ትስሕበኒ<choice><sic>፤</sic><corr resp="JK">፡</corr></choice>
                        ወታወርደኒ፡ ካእበ<choice><sic>፤</sic><corr resp="JK">፡</corr></choice> 
                                <del rend="overUnderlined">ሐ</del><add place="above">ኀ</add>በ፡ ዘቀዳሚ፡ መርገም፤</l>
                    <l n="2">ለዘተወለድነ፡ በሥጋ፡ ወደም፤</l><pb n="2r"/>
                    <l n="3">ዘአእመራሰ፡ ጠቢብ፡ <sic>ላባዊ</sic><choice><sic>፤</sic><corr resp="JK">፡</corr></choice>
                        ለሕልፈት፡ ዛቲ፡ ዓለም፤</l>
                    <l n="4">ፍ<choice><sic>ደ</sic><corr resp="JK">ዳ</corr></choice>፡ 
                        ወይን፡ ይስተይ<choice><sic>፤</sic><corr resp="JK">፡</corr></choice> 
                        ማየ፡ ዝናም፤
                    </l>
                    <l n="5">ወህየንተ፡ ልብስ<choice><sic>፤</sic><corr resp="JK">፡</corr></choice> 
                        ይትከደን፡ ቈጽለ፡ አእዋም፤
                    </l>
                    <l n="6">እስመ፡ ዛቲ፡ ጽላሎት፡ ወሕልም<add place="inline">(</add>ት<add place="inline">)</add>።</l>
                </ab>
            </div>
